  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK608">
<l>maṭimai kuṭimaikkaṭ ṭaṅkiṟṟaṉ ṉoṉṉārk</l>
<l>kaṭimai pukutti viṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If idleness take up its abode in a king of high birth, it will make him a slave of his enemies.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
